PODCAST LINKING RULES:
- To ADD an existing podcast as a new step: create a step with step_type "podcast" AND set podcast_ref to the number above (e.g. podcast_ref: 1). This links the audio.
- To LINK an existing podcast to an already-existing step: modify that step and set podcast_ref.
- ALWAYS set podcast_ref when the step corresponds to an AVAILABLE PODCAST. A step with podcast_ref: null has no audio and will require a new generation.
