RULES:
- To MODIFY a step: include its "id" with updated fields
- To ADD a new step: omit "id" (or set to null)
- To REMOVE a step: omit it entirely from the response
- To REORDER: change the position in the array
- Return ALL steps you want to keep (including unmodified ones)

STEP TYPES: watch | read | quiz | discuss | podcast
- podcast: set source_ids (list of source IDs from AVAILABLE SOURCES) and podcast_topic (briefing text)
